Nomasonto Mshoza Maswanganyi's Memorial Service Live From Bassline, Newtown. JOHANNESBURG - The music fraternity, family and friends will pay their respects to late kwaito artist, Mshoza at her memorial service in Newtown on Wednesday. Nomasonto Maswanganyi, popularly known as Mshoza, died last week aged 37. READ: Mshoza: 'I am worth R500,000, think before you ask me out' Her death has been described as a huge loss to the industry and nation. Mshoza is survived by two children.